title: Missions
body: For 4 days I am not getting any missions, what should I do? Somebody can help?

replies.body: Were you talking about Worlds Missions or the new mission that would convert all of your old runes into BE?
World missions, everything is already converted to BE, but I don't get any missions
Ahhh so yea, those missions were only around while Worlds was in progress. Since it's ended and Worlds is over for the year, those missions have ended as well.
same im not getting that dialy first win of the day mission....
